Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to occur after SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average duration of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation until the next activity in each variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and the end of the case

Name: Total elapsed time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants containing both activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total time spent in SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation compared to time spent in SW-Reviewer Agreed within the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and the subsequent decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision, or SW-EIC Minor Revision)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average cycle time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that include at least one reviewer agreement (SW-Reviewer Agreed)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Total time from the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases with multiple reviewer agreements
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in high-frequency variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to be followed by any EIC decision activity, considering only variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases that eventually lead to manuscript acceptance
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and SW-Awaiting EIC Decision compared to the time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Elapsed time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to the final export event (Manuscript Export Succeeded) in accepted manuscripts
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Minimum time for SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to be completed after all required reviewers have agreed (i.e., after the last SW-Reviewer Agreed in a case)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
